OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome patchy cloud and light
OL,6,Frain in the northwest with some gusty
OL,7,Fwinds. Some lower cloud in the
OL,8,Fsouthwest, mostly around coasts.
OL,9,FOtherwise, another very warm for many,
OL,10,Fespecially in the southeast. Cooler
OL,11,Faround coasts with a sea breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStays cloudy and breezy in
OL,14,Fthe northwest with patchy rain.
OL,15,FVariable cloud elsewhere with clear
OL,16,Fspells and light winds. Mist and fog
OL,17,Fin places. A mild night to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
